 video.\n\nThis is the only way to escape.\n\nWhen you find all of them,\nSomething\" will happen. ......", "short_description": "- The \"disaster\" that befalls you when you see it\n\nOne day, a portable SSD was sent to our staff by a person claiming to be Mr. \u00dd.\nIt contained a 360\u00b0 video recording of several interviews with people involved in an attempt to find out the true meaning of a common self-accusatory urban legend, \"You will be cursed if you listen to it.\n\nIn the video, the people involved complain of poor health and unhappiness.\n\nAnd the \"disastrous presence\" that is hidden in plain sight.\n\nThis project reconstructe"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/project-y-2023/#h.16e2qbqtwnwb", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "https://twitter.com/Y_Pro_Common", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/project-y-2023/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "1008279844328894"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["ja"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "6336330603137323"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "368926052504183"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "368926052504183"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1713672000, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "368926052504183"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "Andro